{"tid":755740,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"大家點睇呢部Asus ROG Strix SCAR II GL504","createTime":"2018-07-25T12:24:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-26T15:37:41.000Z","uid":1487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"a6af917bfaf8c6d334623ec4b6378b9de2a5ddf1","tid":755740,"uid":1487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T12:24:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/dp/B07D7P4SY1/ref=twister_B07DQ4YKRC?_encoding=UTF8&amp;th=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB07D7P4SY1%2Fref%3Dtwister_B07DQ4YKRC%3F_encoding%3DUTF8%26th%3D1&d=O3GdHONW6uTLcbHmVovOSMVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=08bf659f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.amazon.com/dp/B07D7P4SY1/ref=twister_B07DQ4YKRC?_encoding=UTF8&amp;th=1</a><br />\n(Asus ROG Strix SCAR II GL504)<br />\n<br />\n呢隻好似係新出既款黎<br />\n<br />\nAmazon 1070版本賣2000usd<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁對比另一隻同類型既MSI GS65<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/MSI-GS65-Stealth-THIN-054-i7-8750H/dp/B07BBJKCYG/ref=sr_1_1?s=electronics&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;qid=1532520481&amp;sr=1-1&amp;keywords=MSI+GS65+8RF\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FMSI-GS65-Stealth-THIN-054-i7-8750H%2Fdp%2FB07BBJKCYG%2Fref%3Dsr_1_1%3Fs%3Delectronics%26ie%3DUTF8%26qid%3D1532520481%26sr%3D1-1%26keywords%3DMSI%2BGS65%2B8RF&d=O3GdHONW6uTLcbHmVovOSMVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=67c5bb16\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.amazon.com/MSI-GS65-Stealth-THIN-054-i7-8750H/dp/B07BBJKCYG/ref=sr_1_1?s=electronics&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;qid=1532520481&amp;sr=1-1&amp;keywords=MSI+GS65+8RF</a><br />\n<br />\n咁呢隻就賣貴多100幾usd spec方面就幾乎一模一樣<br />\n<br />\n同埋重量方面會輕少少 但呢方面我冇所謂<br />\n<br />\n<strong>所以就想問各位巴打:</strong><br />\n<br />\n1.Asus gaming notebook有冇伏?定係買返msi穩陣d?<br />\n<br />\n2.散熱方面邊隻會好d?<br />\n<br />\n3.除咗呢2部 大家仲有冇類似既laptop推薦? 重啲都冇所謂 (有144hz同散熱好既最好)<br />\n<br />\n多謝各位巴打解答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c546a856744fea1365fbb10e972b21172b43bf90","tid":755740,"uid":1487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T12:24:58.000Z","msg":"推 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0057769cc2b70d6d8089ae717dcbed0eced99e0","tid":755740,"uid":36459,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T12:31:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7dea150e3d4467bb2c04018df739f6c70baf4c01","tid":755740,"uid":1487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c0057769cc2b70d6d8089ae717dcbed0eced99e0","tid":755740,"uid":36459,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T12:31:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T12:32:40.000Z","msg":"好 多謝巴打 我再研究吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f747037ffb0a9c7179b14dfbac1089db8edd123","tid":755740,"uid":36459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T12:37:00.000Z","msg":"GL504 1070唔送香港，要轉運/另一個賣家，1年國際保(包香港)<br />\n<br />\nGS65 香港行貨至有本地保養，amazon買=無保"},{"pid":"20f4c8f9b242435c08aa653c04588f4f2d2ab34b","tid":755740,"uid":1487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0f747037ffb0a9c7179b14dfbac1089db8edd123","tid":755740,"uid":36459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T12:37:00.000Z","msg":"GL504 1070唔送香港，要轉運/另一個賣家，1年國際保(包香港)<br />\n<br />\nGS65 香港行貨至有本地保養，amazon買=無保"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T12:41:41.000Z","msg":"但條link話deliver to Hong Kong既<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁真係冇理由揀GS65了"},{"pid":"646602f2d7d6b1eaf256fcbe055bd3cae995ded6","tid":755740,"uid":70073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T12:44:07.000Z","msg":"上newegg買 <br />\n但係得512Gb ssd <br />\n寄到HK"},{"pid":"6581174453addc5f1002937a2f801e255880228e","tid":755740,"uid"